# fmc_ipv4_prefix_list (Data Source)

This data source reads the IPv4 Prefix List.

## Example Usage

```terraform
data "fmc_ipv4_prefix_list" "example" {
  id = "76d24097-41c4-4558-a4d0-a8c07ac08470"
}
```
